Name: Average time from Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE to Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Average time between Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR and Request Payment
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Request Payment'

Name: Total time from Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION to Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Average resolution time of Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR cases
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR and the end of the case

Name: Minimum time from Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR to Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE for re-submission

Name: Average time it takes from Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR to Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER'

Name: Total resolution time for cases involving Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR followed by Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER'

Name: Minimum time between Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR and Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Average time from Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR to the next activity in the process
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR and the end of the case

Name: Total time for all activities to be completed after Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR and the end of the case

Name: Average waiting time to Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR from the start of the case
Metric: The average of the duration between the start of the case and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Total time it takes for a case to be closed after Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR and the end of the case

Name: Average time for Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR in cases where it leads to a re-submission versus cases leading to case closure
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR and the end of the case

Name: Minimum resolution time of cases with Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR followed by Payment Handled
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Payment Handled'

Name: Average time from Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR to Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER in the same case
